It will not be on the market in the first months of 2009, but probably at the end of the year, if not even in 2010.
Microsoft will certainly try to launch Windows 7 and Windows Mobile 7 together.
The mobile phone, after all, is becoming more and more of a computer.
But the delay, with Android and the iPhone already on the market, is a penalty.
