We, on the contrary, want to look further and deeper, to work seriously on the development of Rome and its future".
The Mayor of Rome also pointed out that 'this Commission is neither a useless body nor a dead body: it is absolutely free, it will not cost the citizens of Rome a single euro and it will serve to reason and to involve the best minds in the capital'.
